archiefmat.scope: Seems to contain mainly received correspondence forwarded to the Governor and also outgoing correspondence.
archiefmat.notes: The data presented are based on a draft of the inventory of the archive (December 2008); numbers of the documents may change in the final version. The complete series up to February 1912 consists of 89 nos.
archiefmat.Aantekeningen:
Gegevens ontleend aan concept-inventaris; nummering stukken kan nog wijzigen.

In verband met zeer slechte staat maar een klein deel bekeken (HJ December 2008)
